                <h2 style="font-size:24px; font-weight:700; color:#000;">V. Thông tin liên hệ</h2>

                <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0;">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-phone me-2"></i> Hotline: <strong>0909 123 456</strong></li>
                    <li><i class="far fa-envelope me-2"></i> Email: <a href="mailto:shopkidora@gmail.com">shopkidora@gmail.com</a></li>
